---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Opinions
description: Hot takes, columns, and analysis on the gaming industry from The Patch.
category: opinions
pagination:
  data: collections.opinions
  size: 12
  alias: posts
permalink: "/opinions/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page/{{ pagination.pageNumber }}/{% endif %}"
---
<header class="page-header">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="badge badge-opinions">opinions</span>
    <h1>Opinions</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--paper-dim);">Columns and hot takes on where gaming is headed — argue with us on X.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="section" style="border-bottom:none;">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="grid">
      {% for post in posts %}
      {% include "partials/card.njk" %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
